---
@version: [2, current]
@description: Disable automatic view path based on ID by specifying a file path to it.
@lot: string $id, string $path
@static: 1
@example: |
  Content::get('foo.bar'); // [^1]
  Content::set('foo.bar', '.\lot\asset\php\view.php'); // [^2]
  Content::get('foo.bar'); // [^3]

  // [^1]: Prints nothing.
  // [^2]: Set!
  // [^3]: Prints the contents of `.\lot\asset\php\view.php` file.
